headline: The Campbell’s Company Board Elects Mary Alice Dorrance Malone Jr. as Director
summary: CAMDEN, N.J., July 18, 2025--The Campbell's Company (NASDAQ:CPB) today announced that the company’s Board of Directors has elected Mary Alice Dorrance Malone Jr. as a member of the Board. Malone, 42, is the Founder and Chief Brand Director of Malone Souliers, an international luxury fashion brand.
